      <title>香港上诉法院推翻北京方正维好债券裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/hk-appeal-court-overturns-peking-founder-keepwell-bond-rulings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港一家法院推翻了早先的法庭判决，裁定北大方正集团有限公司（北大方正集团前身为北大方正的商业部门）违反了其子公司美元债券中承诺向父母提供经济支持的维好条款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/hk-appeal-court-overturns-peking-founder-keepwell-bond-rulings</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 02:43:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国建设银行因再保险欺诈损失在美国被起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/china-construction-bank-sued-in-us-over-reinsurance-fraud-losses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国第三大商业银行中国建设银行在美国的一项诉讼中被指控在再保险行业实施大规模欺诈，导致公司遭受“巨大损失”并导致股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/china-construction-bank-sued-in-us-over-reinsurance-fraud-losses</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 02:41:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>监管机构考虑豁免股息税，香港股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/hong-kong-stocks-rise-as-regulators-consider-dividend-tax-waiver</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港股市上涨，据称监管机构正在考虑一项提议，免除个人投资者通过沪港通购买港股所赚取的股息税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/hong-kong-stocks-rise-as-regulators-consider-dividend-tax-waiver</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 01:37:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Vanguard 与 Pimco 一起认为日本央行加息幅度高于市场幅度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/vanguard-joins-pimco-in-seeing-more-boj-rate-hikes-than-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[先锋集团 (Vanguard Group Inc.) 的阿莱斯·考特尼 (Ales Koutny) 表示，市场低估了日本央行今年需要采取多强硬的政策立场才能提振日元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/vanguard-joins-pimco-in-seeing-more-boj-rate-hikes-than-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 00:15:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通表示印度指数纳入已步入正轨，客户已做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/jpmorgan-says-india-index-inclusion-on-track-most-clients-ready</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通全球指数研究主管表示，摩根大通计划从 6 月份开始将印度纳入其新兴市场债务指数，尽管存在一些“初期问题”，但大多数客户已准备好进行交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/jpmorgan-says-india-index-inclusion-on-track-most-clients-ready</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 23:30:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于对美国降息的乐观情绪重燃，油价延续两天涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价连续第三天上涨——让它走上每周收益的轨道——美国就业数据支持美联储今年降息，提振了风险资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-09/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-10</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 23:26:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
